<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>PRESS-SIM is a simple simulation tool that helps shaping a press die. This enables a quick understanding of ‘Blank Deployment Lines’ and ‘Flange Development Lines (Trim Development Lines)’ that will help quotations at the initial stage of design.</p><p>Also, the capabilities of decreasing thickness ratio and analyzing cracks and wrinkles enable quick detections of poor shapes.</p><p> </p><h5><strong>Features</strong></h5><ul><li><u><strong>Command about Blank Deployment Lines</strong></u></li></ul><p>This command enables a quick creation of lines/curves that express the outlines of a modelled shape on a plane surface</p><ul><li>Blank Deployment</li></ul><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/03.PRESS-SIM/PRESS_SIM_01.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><ul><li>Thickness decreasing ratio</li></ul><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/03.PRESS-SIM/PRESS_SIM_02.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><ul><li>Analyses of cracks and wrinkles</li></ul><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/03.PRESS-SIM/PRESS_SIM_03.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><ul><li><u><strong>Command for Flange Deployment Lines</strong></u></li></ul><p>This command enables a quick creation of flange curves/lines for dies in accordance with a shape of product.</p><ul><li>Flange Deployment Lines (Deployment lines for trimming)</li></ul><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/03.PRESS-SIM/PRESS_SIM_04.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div></div></div></div></div>